landing.noapp: Karekau koe e hiahia he taupānga hei whakamahi i {{ BRAND }} i runga i to waea, papa ranei! He pai te mahi a te paetukutuku i runga waea pūkoro.
landing.intro: {{BRAND}} ({{TRANSLITERATION}}) he huarahi pai ki te tutaki i nga hoa hou. Ina whakamahi koe i te {{ BRAND }}, ka kowhiria e matou tetahi atu i runga i te matapōkere ka tuku koe ki te korero kotahi-ki-tetahi. Hei awhina i a koe ki te noho haumaru, ko nga korerorero he ingoamuna mena ka korero koe ki tetahi ko wai koe (kaore i te tūtohutia!), a ka taea e koe te whakamutu i te korerorero i nga wa katoa. Tirohia a maatau <6>Tuhinga me nga tikanga</6>, me <8>Aratatohu Hapori</8> mo nga korero mo nga mahi me nga mea e mahia ana mo te whakamahi {{ BRAND }}. {{ BRAND }} he AI ​​whakaōrite te kōrerorero ataata engari karekau he whakaōrite e tino tika ana. Ko nga kaiwhakamahi anake te kawenga mo o raatau whanonga i a raatau e whakamahi ana i {{ BRAND }}
landing.disclaimer: <0>Me 18 koe (te nuinga ture ranei i to mana whakahaere) pakeke ake ranei hei whakamahi i {{BRAND}}</0>. Tirohia a {{BRAND}} <4>Tuhinga me nga tikanga</4> mo etahi atu korero. Ko nga whakamarumaru a nga matua ka awhina pea i nga maatua kei te waatea i te hokohoko ka kitea etahi atu korero kei <6>https://www.connectsafely.org/controls</6> me etahi atu pae.
landing.pleaseleave: Tena koa waiho mai i a Omay.live ka toro atu ki tetahi waahi pakeke mena koinei te mea e rapu ana koe a he 18 koe (te nuinga ture ranei o to mana whakahaere) pakeke ake ranei.
landing.termscheck: Ma te taki i te pouaka ka whakaae koe kua arotakehia e koe he whakaaetanga kia herea e {{BRAND}}<3>Tuhinga me nga tikanga</3>, <5>Kaupapahere tūmataiti</5> me <7>aratohu Hapori</7>.
landing.agecheck: Kare pea koe e whakamahi i tenei ratonga mena kei raro koe i te 18 tau, te pakeke ranei o te nuinga o te ture i to mana whakahaere. Tirohia a maatau <1>Tuhinga me nga tikanga</1> mo etahi atu korero. <3>Ma te taki i te pouaka ka whakaae koe ka tohu koe he 18 ou tau (te nuinga ture ranei i to mana whakahaere) pakeke ake ranei.</3>

cookies.message: Ka whakamahi matou i nga pihikete hei whakapai ake i to wheako i runga i te papanga, engari ka taea e koe te whakaputa-waho. Ma tenei mahi <1>ka kite koe i nga panui i nga wa katoa</1> i te mea kaore e taea e matou te whai i te mea kua kite koe i a raatau, kaore ranei.

alerts.banreason: Na te kino o te whanonga. Kaua e māharahara, e kore e mau tonu te aukati.

error.adblocker: Kaore e taea e matou te tuku i a koe ki te mahi i tera na te mea kei te whakamahi koe i te Kaihanga Panui
error.disableadblocker: <0>Ko te tumanako kei te pai koe ki to maatau paetukutuku. Hei whakamahi tonu, ka tono matou ki a koe kia whakakorehia to adblocker. He kore utu to maatau paetukutuku ki te whakamahi, a ko nga panui e whakaatuhia ana i to maatau paetukutuku ka awhina i a maatau ki te utu i nga utu mo te whakahaere i te ratonga. Ma te whakakore i to parenga panui, ka awhina koe i a maatau ki te pupuri i to maatau paetukutuku.</0><1>Mauruuru mo to tautoko!</1>
